    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接<strong>《禁闭》</strong>带来的极致体验——这款FP4（第一人称节奏精准平台游戏）将把你的技巧推向极限。在布满致命陷阱的封闭空间中寻找生路，每一步都至关重要。达什精准的移动与操作机制，正是他克服前方残酷障碍的关键所在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327590/extras/ee87c975f479a16b8c6bf6e447a08528.poster.avif?t=1771605814\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327590/extras/ee87c975f479a16b8c6bf6e447a08528.webm?t=1771605814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327590/extras/ee87c975f479a16b8c6bf6e447a08528.mp4?t=1771605814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>游戏亮点:</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精准操控：</strong>在精心设计的关卡中，掌握每次跳跃与冲刺的技巧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>冲刺机制：</strong>运用冲刺及其变体突破障碍，突破速度极限，以动态策略完成赛道。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>粗犷霓虹环境：</strong>游戏采用震撼的粗犷主义视觉风格，霓虹元素营造独特沉浸氛围，凸显黑暗压抑的设定。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>极限挑战：</strong>挑战约40个精心设计的关卡，考验速度与精准度。以最短时间通关将提升难度并带来高重复游玩价值，为追求激烈刺激体验的玩家量身打造。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327590/extras/2dc54078875bb85629cb7c112daa111b.poster.avif?t=1771605814\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327590/extras/2dc54078875bb85629cb7c112daa111b.webm?t=1771605814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327590/extras/2dc54078875bb85629cb7c112daa111b.mp4?t=1771605814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞技与排名：</strong>游戏引入排名系统激发竞技热情。玩家可争夺榜单巅峰与高分宝座，通过自我挑战与玩家对决角逐排行榜最高荣誉。此机制不仅激发竞技热情，更将玩家推向极限，最终嘉奖最敏捷的顶尖高手。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若你渴望在残酷环境中检验精准操作与敏捷反应，<strong>《禁闭》</strong>正是为你量身打造的游戏！</p>",
